'''Azuma no Kuni Mutsu Hara no Ason''' (東国六腹朝臣) refers to a collective term for the following six clans, all of which claim common origins in the [[Keno Province]] area:

* {{ill|Kamitsukeno no Ason (Kamitsukeno clan)|ja|上毛野朝臣（上毛野氏）|qq=draft|qq=draft}}
* {{ill|Shimotsukeno clan|ja|下毛野朝臣（下毛野氏）|Shimotsukeno clan=Shimotsukeno clan|lt=Shimotsukeno no Ason (Shimotsukeno clan)|qq=draft|qq=draft}}
* {{ill|Ōno no Ason (Ōno clan)|ja|大野朝臣（大野氏）|qq=draft|qq=draft}}
* {{ill|Ikeda no Ason (Ikeda clan)|ja|池田朝臣（池田氏）|qq=draft|qq=draft}}
